              </div>
              <div class="text-block animated-content fade_in animate">
                <p class="regform_p">You can sign up for the giveaway on the <a href="https://www.computingforgood.org/register">Computing for Good website</a>.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-block animated-content fade_in animate">
                <p class="regform_p">Make sure you follow all the instructions on this page (scroll down to the end of the page and fill out the form!). Once you are all set up with WCG and on the Ripple Labs WCG team, the last step is to link your WCG account with your Ripple Wallet on the <a href="https://www.computingforgood.org/register">registration page</a>. You won’t get any XRP for points computed unless you fill out the <a href="https://www.computingforgood.org/register">registration page</a> form.</p>
