              </div>
              <div class="text-block animated-content fade_in animate">
                <p class="regform_p">You can open a Ripple wallet on the <a href="https://ripple.com/client">Ripple website</a>.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-block animated-content fade_in animate">
                <p class="regform_p">Please note, your wallet is only as safe as the password you set. Money in Ripple wallets functions like cash, and anybody who has your password can steal all the money in the wallet. We recommend not re-using any existing passwords you have, and creating a password that has letters, numbers and symbols.</p>
