              </div>
              <div class="text-block animated-content fade_in animate">
                <p class="regform_p">Before you can register for the WCG giveaway you need to join the Ripple Labs team which can be done in two ways. </p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-block animated-content fade_in animate">
              	<p class="regform_p">You can <a href="http://www.worldcommunitygrid.org/team/viewTeamInfo.do?teamId=0QGNJ4D832">join the team</a> or go through the following 4 steps:</p>
                <ol>
	                <li>Log on to your WCG profile</li>
	                <li>Go to “My Contributions”</li>
	                <li>Click on “My Team.” If Ripple Labs is not your team, click on...</li>
	                <li>“Find Team.” Now you should be able to search for and join the Ripple Labs Team.</li>
                </ol>              
